          <h1 class="my-6 text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900">Chi sia stato non si sa</h1>
          <div class="flex justify-center">
            <img
              alt="Spider-man: Across the spider-verse"
              src="spider-man-across-the-spider-verse.jpg"
              class="h-auto max-h-[36rem] w-full"
